p.e:
Your ultimate goal
should be to hold out
as long as possible,
building an impenetrable
fortress and grinding
oil and coins to make
the ULTIMATOR!!!

The hardest part about
this is the Oil, so make
sure to use as few of
it as possible, and to
get as much Oil as
possible!

CHAPTER 6: TIPPS

Conveyor belts are your
best friend.
they allow you to con-
nect gold deposits.

Wallers can build bricky
turrets. make sure to
pair them up with a few
builders though, to get
coins from corpses
